author: Russell Brand
description:
Trump calls him a communist — but is Zoran Mamdani just the latest response to a broken system? In this episode, I dive into Mamdani’s campaign for NYC mayor and what it reveals about America’s political evolution. From Obama to Trump to Mamdani, is the cycle of betrayal and populist backlash finally shifting power back to the people? I explore the contradictions, critiques, and possibilities of democratic socialism in a city on the brink of change.
